    "zh": "全年 11 位不同车手轮流登上分站领奖台最高位，凯克·罗斯伯格仅凭一场分站冠军就以稳定的积分摘得年度车手冠军，是 F1 历史上最动荡的赛季之一。",
    "en": "Eleven different drivers won races in a famously chaotic season; Keke Rosberg needed only a single victory to secure the drivers' title on consistency, one of the most turbulent seasons in F1 history."
